@global.w_crisis_female_caregiver (ecinga): "Khawuthath’ umoya... Ufuna ntoni umntanam? Ufuna ndizole ndize ndiphulaphule" 

@global.w_crisis_female_caregiver: "Yizokuhlala apha ecaleni kwam. Thath’ ixesha lakho, ndiphulaphule.”

