SourceText:
@global.w_rules_female_caregiver_2: "Let’s look together online at how we can keep this fun for you but also safe. Look – you can make your account private and control who follows you.

So you can accept people you know from school and our community, but not people who contact you online.

Can we make a rule together that you can use @global.teen_social_medium, but with a private account? I trust you to know who to accept!”

text:
@global.w_rules_female_caregiver_2: "Makhe sijonge kunye kwi-intanethi ukuze sibone ukuba singaqhubeka njani siqiniseka ukuba wonwabile kodwa ukwakhuselekile. Khangela – ungenza iakhawunti yakho ibe nobumfihlo uze ulawule abantu abakulandelayo.

Ungamkela abantu obaziyo esikolweni nakwindawo esihlala kuyo, kungekhona abantu abaqhagamshelana nawe kwi-intanethi.

Ngaba singawenza kunye umgaqo onokuwusebenzisa @global.teen_social_medium, kodwa kwiakhawunti yabucala? Ndiyathemba uyazi ukuba ngubani omawumamkele!”

